月以上 5 年以下有期徒刑。\r\n施用第二級毒品者，處 3 年以下有期徒刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TYDM/110%2c%e5%a3%a2%e7%b0%a1%2c1197%2c20220123%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TYDM,110,壢簡,1197,20220123,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"壢簡","JNO":"1197","JDATE":"20220123","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例"}